      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a gunshot wound. people saying \"it's not about the money\" doesn't change the fact that my life is over. the debt, the shame... it's just a dead end. i'm just tired of fighting a battle i've already lost. it would be so much quieter if everything just stopped.",
